   140â†’## Project Structure
   142â†’This project is organized as a monorepo using `pnpm` workspaces. The structure is as follows:
   143â†’
   144â†’- **[packages/app-client](./packages/app-client/)**: Frontend application built with SolidJS.
   145â†’- **[packages/app-server](./packages/app-server/)**: Backend application using HonoJS.
   146â†’- **[packages/deploy-cloudflare](./packages/deploy-cloudflare/)**: Cloudflare Pages build scripts and configuration.
   147â†’- **[packages/lib](./packages/lib/)**: Core functionalities of Enclosed.
   148â†’- **[packages/cli](./packages/cli/)**: Command-line interface for Enclosed.
   149â†’
