packages/crypto/README.md
     1â†’# Enclosed crypto library
     3â†’This package contains the natives crypto primitives used by the [Enclosed lib and project](https://enclosed.cc). It is a standalone package built to provide compatibility between different environments by exposing the same API for node:crypto and web SubtleCrypto.
     4â†’
     5â†’## Installation
     7â†’```bash
     8â†’# with npm
     9â†’npm install @enclosed/crypto
    10â†’
    11â†’# with yarn
    12â†’yarn add @enclosed/crypto
    13â†’
    14â†’# with pnpm
    15â†’pnpm add @enclosed/crypto
    16â†’```
    17â†’
    18â†’## License
    22â†’## Credits and Acknowledgements

