     5â†’# How It Works
     7â†’Enclosed is designed with a focus on security and privacy, ensuring that your notes remain confidential from creation to retrieval. This section explains the entire process, from creating a note to decrypting it, highlighting the end-to-end encryption that makes Enclosed a secure platform.
     8â†’
