packages/docs/src/index.md
     5â†’# Enclosed
     7â†’**Enclosed** is a minimalistic web application designed for sending private and secure notes. Whether you need to share sensitive information or just want a simple way to send encrypted messages, Enclosed provides a user-friendly interface with strong security features to ensure your data remains confidential.
     8â†’
     9â†’The name **Enclosed** is inspired by the idea of keeping your notes safe and secure, like a sealed envelope.
    10â†’
    11â†’## Key Features
    27â†’## Why Enclosed?
    33â†’## Get Started

